{"tid":1538540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「若我們接受了政府的條件 我們已死去的朋友是不會原諒我們的」","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:14:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T08:24:44.000Z","uid":161436,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"11e33593eab91cc7839780a4fb163c155aba75c0","tid":1538540,"uid":161436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:14:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">6月9就撤回我諗香港人實收貨<br />\n不過如果一早撤回咗 香港人就唔會醒覺<br />\n<br />\n呢三個月發生嘅事已經唔係一句撤回就可以搞掂<br />\n7位烈士 3隻眼 千幾位手足俾人拘捕受折磨</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">請唔好唔記得6月至今發生嘅每一件事</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yA63W7L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyA63W7L.jpg&h=54aae982&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XUQcQsM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXUQcQsM.jpg&h=16c1c611&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nzQ8oNM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnzQ8oNM.jpg&h=230098bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求 決一不可！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">１。全面撤回逃犯條例<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">同埋要追究721警黑合作 831太子恐襲</span><br />\n仲有一大埋野要逐一清算<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">撤回就想我地收貨？不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WifsEha.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWifsEha.jpg&h=bdd8b754&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6526c4ea72477a0964d11e0524a9041ff6fe0124","tid":1538540,"uid":266362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">大個仔獨立必睇</span></span></span></strong><br />\n［召喚攬炒巴] 星球級反擊！香港最後本錢 VS 赤獸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529054</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">9 大核彈內容包括：</span></span><br />\n(1) 基本法自古以來是中國領土的謬誤<br />\n(2) 中英聯合聲明的謬誤<br />\n(3) 不平等條約無效論是謊言<br />\n(4) 中華民國早已放棄香港的主權<br />\n(5) 中華人民共和國以武力脅迫大英國移交香港主權不合國際法<br />\n(6) 70年代聯合國從非自治領名單剔除香港<br />\n(7) 中英聯合聲明違反住民自決原則<br />\n(8) 香港符合《蒙特維多國家權利及義務公約》中「國家」的定義<br />\n(9) 香港軍事史<br />\n<br />\n請幫推以下post！<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">香港人一定要知！</span></ins></strong></span></span>一定一定要睇！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港史實在此！勿做港豬！想贏就入嚟！</span></span></span></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d98a31f06b556bec55a1a720bbcfcba55868dfd4","tid":1538540,"uid":13349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:15:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a961f0d0c6614890d02b250e8f00633aace3336","tid":1538540,"uid":161436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:15:48.000Z","msg":"認真肯收貨個啲 對唔對得住犧牲咗嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab2c5533c2063f30a43b0ef674726732ebb9b157","tid":1538540,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:15:49.000Z","msg":"不能逆轉！"},{"pid":"de428cfee3011d292624fc40e41ac0a1add47108","tid":1538540,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:15:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd75487f726f4d18d6d16effbad383c8ea4bd92b","tid":1538540,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:16:10.000Z","msg":"撤旦都說接受不了"},{"pid":"2d9af015decaa61c751849caf8a6d5786905492f","tid":1538540,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:16:43.000Z","msg":"大家要到幾時先察覺，靠政府去實現五大訴求已經變成一個好恐怖既局？<br />\n<br />\n[時光倒流Re-post] 香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538204</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先大家可以選擇服用咗以上文章先<br />\n<br />\n然後我可以反問一句，有冇人諗過五大訴求真係實現既情況會係點？<br />\n<br />\n係，的確可能證實到瘋狂既民意係可以改變到政府所作出既決定，但下次兩地一檢呢？再下次智慧燈柱、全面普教中呢？反送中2.0、3.0發生，真係好？點解要跟住個垃圾政權條尾走？<br />\n<br />\n香港人，唔好再「<span style=\"color: red;\">要求</span>」政府畀到五個願望你哋，請大家一齊親手達成依五個，甚至一百個願望都得，可唔可以？<br />\n<br />\n睇唔明我講咩既話請讀上面篇文章一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a5b31b91b8778f7c852e15e6be6ae368a15fad7","tid":1538540,"uid":35514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:17:44.000Z","msg":"撤回條例嘅目的只不過係阻止美國通過香港人權與民主法案 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"c939ba1c8c77cf32e6c38abd54b777f232f77f2f","tid":1538540,"uid":161436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab2c5533c2063f30a43b0ef674726732ebb9b157","tid":1538540,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:15:49.000Z","msg":"不能逆轉！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:18:44.000Z","msg":"返唔到轉頭了<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"266ec095a639105190a39d20e607b0933c208b3f","tid":1538540,"uid":161436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:20:51.000Z","msg":"五大訴求"},{"pid":"5498c66542a7e49817502a151bf8993a127a4d1b","tid":1538540,"uid":161436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:21:03.000Z","msg":"缺一不可"},{"pid":"ff84a1bd63182eca022a73f921edef17d59d237b","tid":1538540,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:21:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8597aa70fe84fa0107dd2d85e07c39c3a771fea7","tid":1538540,"uid":161436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:22:55.000Z","msg":"好驚林奠宣布撤回啲人就冷卻落嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa6450ad9e8bbbd2d63e3d71285d6a3a7ca5a3f0","tid":1538540,"uid":302944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:22:59.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 唔撚收貨呀 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求</span></strong></span> 係五大訴求 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">缺一不可</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"674564a13d116aec8e6584db4e6c34484db20661","tid":1538540,"uid":295304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:23:00.000Z","msg":"有冇見過兇殺案由政府新聞處公佈？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535010\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535010</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n睇埋回覆先留言，因為分析我放咗喺回覆<br />\n<br />\n成個熱門勁多都係講林鄭撤回嘅風，<br />\n但而家佢撤唔撤回都好，831太子站有冇死人、有冇極嚴重傷勢受害人，呢d都係要查啊！唔好俾佢轉移焦點啊！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好認真，點解一路發生咁多件事，都冇話撤回，突然今日會講起？到底呢幾日發生咗咩事逼到佢要做野？係咪真係其實死咗人？就算冇死人，到底情況係幾嚴重？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要求黨鐵交出831太子站完整CCTV記錄啊！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"42a06ef94c9cf7d6d7bea2df9e33cc625a5c8ee2","tid":1538540,"uid":161436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa6450ad9e8bbbd2d63e3d71285d6a3a7ca5a3f0","tid":1538540,"uid":302944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:22:59.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 唔撚收貨呀 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求</span></strong></span> 係五大訴求 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">缺一不可</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:23:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無錯<br />\n依家撤回都唔會降溫"},{"pid":"71f63dfdcd702fb5d86ee111e8188a8f42d09cd3","tid":1538540,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:25:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong><em><div style=\"text-align: center;\">毋忘七烈 千一義 四眼 三十骨折 手腳筋<br />\n721元朗 811警暴 831車廂 雙肺 一裙<br />\n無數屈辱私刑 重傷昏迷<br />\n<br />\n撤回 定性 釋士 究警 普選</div></em></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">港共殺人政權企圖以錄音、撤回<br />\n轉移<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">太子地鐵傷亡、六警壓脊椎休克昏迷、<br />\n新屋嶺、民主人權法案</span></strong>事件焦點<br />\n醒呀大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 政府帶緊風向<br />\n背後繼續大清算 入獄 利刑 一年後被失蹤</span>"},{"pid":"2d5c9fd1b173a3e4feee2e8b2129a9f7fb799bbc","tid":1538540,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a961f0d0c6614890d02b250e8f00633aace3336","tid":1538540,"uid":161436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:15:48.000Z","msg":"認真肯收貨個啲 對唔對得住犧牲咗嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:31:37.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n義士不是condom"},{"pid":"0105b04e283fba9118ac78e6155ecdfaf4c98af7","tid":1538540,"uid":161436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d5c9fd1b173a3e4feee2e8b2129a9f7fb799bbc","tid":1538540,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a961f0d0c6614890d02b250e8f00633aace3336","tid":1538540,"uid":161436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:15:48.000Z","msg":"認真肯收貨個啲 對唔對得住犧牲咗嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:31:37.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n義士不是condom"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:34:11.000Z","msg":"無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5717fd89a5fffb3ecdef196e2d4f21034a356bef","tid":1538540,"uid":276150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:37:23.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可！<br />\n解散警隊 沒收宿舍 停止發放薪金"},{"pid":"12202a40b0974accd35efa53d0be3bfb6e512084","tid":1538540,"uid":161436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5717fd89a5fffb3ecdef196e2d4f21034a356bef","tid":1538540,"uid":276150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:37:23.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可！<br />\n解散警隊 沒收宿舍 停止發放薪金"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:37:59.000Z","msg":"解散警隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a214e5e781fbd7f30fd605f2a9de04a95c816d3","tid":1538540,"uid":71446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:39:15.000Z","msg":"咁都接受既話，受傷害既香港人同義士一定唔會原諒！"},{"pid":"04f4f802c03902203fcbdb58c7f1bcb353721e23","tid":1538540,"uid":161436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a214e5e781fbd7f30fd605f2a9de04a95c816d3","tid":1538540,"uid":71446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:39:15.000Z","msg":"咁都接受既話，受傷害既香港人同義士一定唔會原諒！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:41:52.000Z","msg":"絕對唔可以俾佢 撤回 兩隻字<br />\n令社會氣氛同呢場運動降溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8507206f42bba61ae26db02ad915e899d1e30602","tid":1538540,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:46:43.000Z","msg":"既然壽終正寢都可以變返暫緩，出自含莖長官把口嘅&quot;撒回&quot;，其實都可能在立法會重開嘅時候，繼續進行二讀同三讀<br />\n<br />\n條閪婆純粹係想試水温，如果商界代表話接受撒回，政府就扮準備撒回修例 (順便拖埋商界落水)，實際就準備下一步行動，大圍捕參與遊行 / 示威嘅人士 (和理非 &amp; 勇武)，試圖在十月一日前，將香港粉飾到好似好太平咁，之後就大清算<br />\n<br />\n所以，除咗要含莖長官確實落實五大訴求之外，亦需要各位有法律認知嘅人，幫手入稟控告含莖長官在今次事件疏忽 (例如濫用修例去處理單一案件，沒有確保黑犬嚴格遵守處理遊行嘅條例同守則，亦沒有使用可行的方法，去核實被羈留者享有基本嘅人權)"}]}